  "body": "BftMiningAcceptanceTest is currently only testing byzantiumBlock.\n\nWe want to update the BFT acceptanceTests (or integrationTests if more appropriate) to cover Berlin, London and ideally free gas networks as well.\n\n## Suggested Acceptance Criteria \n\n// Given network is Berlin and paid-gas\n// Then blocks are produced\n// And can send a frontier transaction with enough gas to cover minGasPrice\n\n// Given network is Berlin and free-gas\n// Then blocks are produced\n// And can send a frontier transaction with 0 gas\n\n// Given network is London and paid-gas\n// Then blocks are produced\n// And can send an eip1559 transaction with enough gas to cover baseFee\n\n// Given network is London and free-gas (using zeroBaseFee: true)\n// Then blocks are produced\n// And can send an eip1559 transaction with 0 gas",
